# Acceptance Criteria: Merge Gate

Atlas must complete all criteria before the integration is considered done.

## Pre-Merge Verification

- [ ] PR state retrieved successfully
- [ ] All required CI status checks verified
- [ ] No merge conflicts detected
- [ ] PR is in mergeable state

## CI Status Checks

- [ ] All GitHub Actions workflows passed (green)
- [ ] Required status checks are satisfied
- [ ] No failing checks that would block merge

## Merge Execution

{{#if merge_enabled}}
- [ ] Merge operation executed successfully
- [ ] Target branch updated with PR changes
- [ ] PR state changed to merged
{{else}}
- [ ] Merge eligibility confirmed
- [ ] Report generated for manual merge
{{/if}}

## Post-Merge

{{#if delete_branch}}
- [ ] Source branch deleted after successful merge
{{/if}}
- [ ] Merge status reported back to Linear/GitHub
- [ ] No errors during merge process
